Last time we used it, the router worked fine and was configured with the latest VH-109 Access Point firmware (for FMS like usage).
Now, it’s lighting up, solid power light, blank Sys light, and rio light on (though no rio is connected).
A computer doesn’t recognize connection when connected to it via a wire.
Also, all the Ethernet ports light up, even though no Ethernet cable is connected to most of them.
Any clue why might this be happening, and how one could solve this?

(Picture for reference, stuck like that for multiple minutes already)
